<div class='home'>
  <h1 class='title'>About This Website</h1>
  <div class='home-component'>
    <h2 class='sub-title'>Our mission</h2>
    <div class='misson'>
      <div>
        <p>
          This website is created to help bridge the communication between
          diabetes patient and their clinicians. The patients can use this
          website to easily record their own health data. The clinicians can
          manage multiple patients and support them through positive messages.
        </p>
      </div>

      <img src='./images/misson-img.gif' id='misson-img' />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='home-component' id='use-guidance'>
    <h2 class='sub-title'>How to use</h2>
    <p>Most of this site's functions required you to be logged in.</p>
    <div class='users'>
      <div class='user'>
        <div class='user-text' id='patients-text'>
          <h2 class='sub-title'>Patients</h2>
          <img src='./images/patient-img.gif' />
          <p>
            <b>Please contact your clinician for registration</b>. The clinician
            will ask you for more details and fill the registration form. They
            then should give you your account information comprised of email and
            password. The email will be what you give them, but the password
            will be something basic like '123456'.
            <b>Please login and change your password as soon as possible</b>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='user' id='clinicians'>
        <div class='verticle-line'></div>
        <div class='user-text' id='clinicians-text'>
          <h2 class='sub-title'>Clinicians</h2>
          <img src='./images/clinician-img.gif' />
          <p>
            You can register directly on this website.
            <b>You are also responsible for adding patients to your account to
              manage</b>. After added the patient, you can specify which health
            data you want the patient to record. The website has features that
            allow you to send supportive messages and to be notified when
            patients has dangerous measurements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='home-component' id='startup-intro'>
    <h2 class='sub-title'>About us</h2>
    <p>
      We are a new medical startup based in Melbourne that want to help change
      the world into a better place.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>